{"tid":1404040,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國媒體最緊張三樣野：國旗、國徽、鬼佬","createTime":"2019-08-04T02:06:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T04:03:20.000Z","uid":76591,"like":68,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"84abc99368afec89ab60cc68ceab05ee99073943","tid":1404040,"uid":76591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T02:06:37.000Z","msg":"強國親戚發現一個好有趣既現象<br />\n香港幾多百萬人遊行示威佢未必會報<br />\n但若果國旗國徽出事，佢地一定報<br />\n<br />\n琴日尖沙咀支國旗游水，好快就見到報導<br />\n連香港獨立旗都寫埋，今次大家成功了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tgxBPCj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtgxBPCj.jpg&h=66bf065d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，遊行示威見到外國國旗，或者有外國人參與隊伍，又係一定報<br />\n<br />\n美國旗、英國旗、香港旗，乜都好，以後大家show多幾支<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>光復香港，時代革命</strong>"},{"pid":"8e4da89eef2dac23b048c8ffe8f0df10c92cdd86","tid":1404040,"uid":187796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T02:51:58.000Z","msg":"我會罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b46a5d362740e686c53ff1562412b359abc9344c","tid":1404040,"uid":16057,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T02:54:16.000Z","msg":"咁除左掛香港獨立之外 不如掛埋其他敏感字眼/反共資訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34fd015d5d88bb1784862c30c16624de9c11bf63","tid":1404040,"uid":227801,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b46a5d362740e686c53ff1562412b359abc9344c","tid":1404040,"uid":16057,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T02:54:16.000Z","msg":"咁除左掛香港獨立之外 不如掛埋其他敏感字眼/反共資訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T02:55:51.000Z","msg":"係囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cada8a50cdf5adab5d6c69fe95d6d21759ae6638","tid":1404040,"uid":186,"like":2,"disli